src=3D"Screen_Troops_files/image005.png" align=3Dright hspace=3D12 v:shapes=
=3D"Picture_x0020_0"><![endif]><span
style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Recruiting Troops directly<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Troops can also be re=
cruited
directly at colonies in the main screen. Select your colony and click the
&#8220;Recruit Troops&#8221; Action button under the Selection Panel.<o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>You can also recruit =
troops
using the popup menu that appears when you right-click one of your colonies.
Click the option to &#8220;Recruit Troops&#8221; in the popup menu.</span><=
/p>

